Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the miracle that is going \Nto happen under the moonlight tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You claim that when the crime occurred,\N three days ago at 1:00 pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you were on Mt. Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a souvenir photograph with a \Nclock in the background to back it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this photo was \Ntaken at 3:44:58.22 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock had been messed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:47.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The length of the shadows \Nindicates the correct time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:02.41,Signs - readability,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}The famous detective is just back from London, \Nbut has already solved a case!\NThere it is! His famous line: \N"Everything has come to light."\NShould Kid the Phantom Thief watch his back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything has come to light," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't stop with that arrogant catchphrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The showdown between him and Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:17.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's gonna \Nhave a showdown with Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector! There's a new \Nadvance notice from Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:07.28,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}A Great Detective Comes to Light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:12.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Pecasso Exhibition  {sic}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's {\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are handling it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Little do they know that \NI'm gonna steal it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Inspector Nakamori must be \Nresponsible for this tight security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But not even Buddha realizes \Nthat I'm observing them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,from way over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't know that famous tagline?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the famous detective \Nwho just got back from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do I care about that crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris, London, or wherever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna humor you playing detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? You're the one \Nwho invited me here, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only because the expression on your face \Nwas practically begging me to invite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make that kind of face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, Kai-troll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:29.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this why you said the rink's condition \Nwas bad today and clung to the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:34.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "Aoko-sama, please,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm never gonna beg you like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii-chan's info better be on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While searching for information on \Nthe Big Jewels, as you requested,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came across something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0} is definitely a \Nmasterpiece of abstract art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:23.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's valued at 400 million, \Nwhich doesn't quite add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The prevailing view is that Pecasso used \Na special kind of paint for this part,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's actually more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief said he'd be here\N at 10:00 pm on the dot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, synchronize your watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, right now, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,2015 CE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,February 3rd, Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,8:50:16.05 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch is never off more \Nthan 0.001 seconds in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're the guy that just \Ngot back from London...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hakuba Saguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:17.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost! This is no place for amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Nakamori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a hard-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Commissioner Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my son. Unfortunately, all this \Nmedia adulation has gone to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:36.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping you'll show him up here so he \Nlearns just how tough a crime scene can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, leave it to me, Nakamori Ginzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's my great inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got any questions, \Nfeel free to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kid the Phantom Thief's gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Male, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When was he born?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his blood type?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of women does he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of cologne does he wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Favorite cologne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.18,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Height?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How tall is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does he weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Body type?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his body type?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his hairstyle? His hobbies? \NHis favorite baseball team?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.44,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Favorite baseball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The snow's really comin' down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate workin' when it's freezing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is swarming with cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get where you're supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A police badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.58,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}I took the painting.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He must still be in the vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:59.47,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the painting.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, should I really take {\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0} now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm surprised they fell \Nfor such a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an extremely elementary trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When something isn't where \Nit's supposed to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,people assume that it's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sensory trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even magic shows use them these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one minute, 13.02 seconds late,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got held up by the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:46.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you weren't so quick on \Nthe uptake with this trick, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I cut your rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the magic show, did you \Nintend to perform a circus act?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I set free the ad balloon \Nthat was on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no escape route now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief, \Ntrue identity unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's time for everything \Nabout you to come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Secrets{\i0} are everything to a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let mine come \Nto light that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A hang glider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Batman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Batman is a comic book hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a north by northwest wind tonight,\N seven on the wind scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not conducive to night flights...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He split into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Which is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Kid would \Nbe terrible at skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This saves me, but I'm not \Nreally happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A balloon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kid the Phantom Thief \Nis bad at ice skating."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your \Ngreat detective fresh from London?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Kid got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.68,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief Steals Adam's Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,February 4th, 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At 9:32.41,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I transfered here from \Na high school in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That way of speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba Saguru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hakuba Saguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba Saguru
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:11.29,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Hidden treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate, but don't look \Nso disappointed, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't forget my poker face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So is everything ready for \Nthe next one, Jii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid will be on TV tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear? Kid the Phantom Thief \Nwill be live on TV tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome! I've gotta record it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.64,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief's \Nscene of the crime on live TV
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcasting live, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get more good luck as \Na robber than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I entered a contest to try to win \NAround the World concert tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You won, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pair of tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face totally gives it away, dingbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?! Talk to me like that,\N and I won't invite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're in a spot \Nof trouble, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hakuba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 180 centimeters tall. \NI weigh 65 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:54.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born on August 29th, 1997.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Virgo. And if you don't\Nmind that I'm blood type A,{smp: originally "if you mind that I'm blood type A" which seemed like it was missing the "don't" but this could also be a mixed up rewrite, TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who thoughtlessly refuses an \Noffer from a lady isn't worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even catch Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A mediocre detective and a \Nmediocre inspector's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve each other! {smp: and also you are a poopyhead!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he's partial to Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:31.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do this. If I capture Kid tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you catch Kid, let's go \Nto the concert together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody like you is gonna catch the \Nunbeatable Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, Kid is a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be an easy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I do happen to lose, \NI'll leave escorting Aoko-kun to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go to the concert,\N but you've got a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the guards here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, this is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess statue that Kid \Nannounced he's going to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a rat could sneak \Nin here, let alone Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Idiots! Catch that vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is in fine form, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, let's interview the detective who's \Nbeen in the spotlight lately, Hakuba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Hakuba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've kind of got a personal stake\N in tonight's showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... What an arrogant jackass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, you third-rate detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:05.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I letting you go \Non a date with Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even Kid can get scared off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many guards are posted underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's posted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The basement's protected \Nby a myriad of sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Kid is stupid enough \Nto try and get in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet they never figured I'd come up \Nthrough the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Four minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Kid really show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you rooting for?\N Hakuba-kun? Or Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hakuba-kun, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? If he wins, you can't \Ngo to the concert with Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't need to go with {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A mediocre detective and a mediocre \Ninspector's daughter! You deserve each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is just putting on \Nthe finishing touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as you get, \NKid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we lower the \Ncurtain on this circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sleeping gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The circus finale is a smoke screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:59.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In 17.58 seconds, this whole \Nroom will be filled with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ten seconds away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an interloper in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's 25 centimeters away from the mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 20 centimeters away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're moving at the same speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:39.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kid? Aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I caught Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Hakuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba-kun, how did it feel to capture Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was a cinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:11.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just... time for me \Nto make my getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector! Kid isn't in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Detective Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculations, I definitely \Nshould've reached it before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief has appeared at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't move if I were you, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusually menacing, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's job is a little personal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Personal? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't what I'm looking for, \Nthen there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori Protects \Nthe Goddess Statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to keep it stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like more painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All traces of the gas will be out of my body \Nin three hours, 31 minutes, and 49 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's performance featured a thief \Nand a detective crossing swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:52.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "magician" has two meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is an illusionist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, an entertainer who performs tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the second is a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class has a new student, Koizumi Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Medieval Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but is she really a witch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:53.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet Seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Scarlet Seduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
